Invocation Name: bayview solutions tracker
des:
The purpose of this skill is to record neighborhood problems in Bayview-Hunter's Point neighborhood of San Francisco, California, USA. This skill allows users to report neighborhood issues such as potholes, graffiti, trash, debris, encampments etc to Bayview Solutions Tracker.

A local patrol is dispatched to ascertain the validity of the issue. If the issue is valid, it is then reported at : https://bayview.solutionstracker.org/map and its resolution tracked.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
